OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Forever chemicals' still  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin use in UK make-up       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Major beauty brands Urban Decay,       
OL,6, Revolution and Inglot are selling      
OL,7, make-up in the UK containing "forever  
OL,8, chemicals", BBC News has found.        
OL,10,FThese pollutants - known as PFAS - have
OL,11,Fbeen linked to serious health concerns 
OL,12,Fincluding cancer.                      
OL,14,FThey are not illegal in the UK but five
OL,15,FEuropean countries are expected to     
OL,16,Fpropose an EU-wide ban on Friday.      
OL,18,FL'Oreal, which owns Urban Decay, told  
OL,19,Fthe BBC it was "well underway" with    
OL,20,Fphasing out the chemicals.             
